      • addUserDefinedLocalSet

        public void addUserDefinedLocalSet​(RvtUserDefinedLocalSet localset)
        Add a user defined local set to this RvtLocalSet.

        The user defined local set must contain a RvtUserDefinedMetadataKey.NumericId. This is required by ST0806, and is used to differentiate between the various user defined local sets nested within this RVT local set.

        Parameters:
        localset - the user defined local set to add

      • addPointOfInterestLocalSet

        public void addPointOfInterestLocalSet​(RvtPoiLocalSet localset)
        Add a Point of Interest (POI) local set to this RvtLocalSet.

        The POI local set must contain a RvtPoiMetadataKey.PoiAoiNumber. This is required by ST0806, and is used to differentiate between the various POI local sets nested within this RVT local set.

        Parameters:
        localset - the POI local set to add
